---
import '../styles/app.css'
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-Hant-TW">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#143b63" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <title>租賃住宅管理人員題庫</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main id="app" aria-live="polite"></main>
    <script>
      const root = document.querySelector<HTMLElement>('#app')!
      const practicePath = '/practice/'
      const renderChoice = () => {
        root.innerHTML = `<section class="question-bank-choice" aria-labelledby="question-bank-heading"><p class="eyebrow">租賃住宅管理人員題庫</p><h1 id="question-bank-heading">選擇題庫</h1><p>請選擇要使用的題庫版本。之後可隨時由頁首返回更換。</p><div class="question-bank-actions"><button type="button" class="button" data-question-bank="withLaw">有詳解題庫</button><button type="button" class="button secondary-button" data-question-bank="withoutLaw">只有答案題庫</button></div><aside class="question-bank-source" aria-labelledby="question-bank-source-heading"><h2 id="question-bank-source-heading">題庫來源與使用說明</h2><p>題庫取自<a href="https://rentalh.org.tw/down-list2.php?lmenuid=12&mpmid=2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">中華民國租賃住宅服務商業同業公會全國聯合會</a>公布的「租賃住宅管理人員資格訓練題庫(全科目不含法源依據)115.02.06更新版」與「租賃住宅管理人員資格訓練題庫(全科目含法源依據)115.02.06更新版」。</p><p class="question-bank-updated">題庫最後更新／轉檔日期：<time datetime="2026-07-21">2026/7/21</time></p><p class="question-bank-disclaimer">本題庫僅供學習與練習使用，內容請以官方最新公告為準。</p><a class="question-bank-about" href="/about/">查看完整資料來源、模擬考規則與免責聲明</a></aside></section>`
        root.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>('[data-question-bank]').forEach((button) => {
          button.addEventListener('click', () => {
            sessionStorage.setItem('rent-exam-question-bank-v1', button.dataset.questionBank!)
            window.location.assign(practicePath)
          })
        })
      }
      renderChoice()
    </script>
    <script>
  import { registerServiceWorker } from '../lib/pwa'

  registerServiceWorker()
</script>
  </body>
</html>
